  <description type="morphology">Plants 1.5–2.5 dm wide. Leaf blades usually round, 0.7–1.2 cm, densely white-lanate, margins not brownish. Scapes erect or nearly so, 3–6 cm, floccose to nearly glabrous. Inflorescences capitate, 1.5–3.5 cm wide; branches absent. Involucres 2–4(–5) per cluster, 5–7 mm. Flowers 5–7 mm; perianth white to cream.</description>
